PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the use by TRANSGAS LIMITED and by SASKATCHEWAN TELECOMMUNICATIONS of their statutory powers to acquire a right-of-way over under and across OKANESE INDIAN RESERVE NO. 82(r), for the purposes of a natural gas pipeline and a telecommunications system, and (b) granting each of those entities an easement for those purposes, in lieu thereof.
